{
  "stem": "3040.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the-- the-- the-- I don't know what the term is to describe the providers who provide the army with food and all this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some medical staff came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of us, of course, were really sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were trying to take care of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they located-- you know, went back into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And to make like a temporary, the best way-- temporary home, the best way we can, they to do-- tried to provide some kind of food compatible to our condition.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this didn't take long for me, because I didn't stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Since this was only seven kilometers from Munich, I walked to Munich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not all myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A few other people who were able to walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there, we got in touch with some authorities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Right away, there were some Germans, and also Americans, set up some offices, some organization, to be able to take care of these refugees of-- of prisoners, you know, camp inmates and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were setting up some kitchens and-- and some barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And also, they took over some hospitals, German hospitals, and the other buildings that they could set up beds and so on for us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But very soon, I was able-- you know, we formed a committee, right away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And very soon, I was able to get an apartment from a German, just threw him out and got an apartment in-- in Munich itself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then they have-- we have really, under the supervision of the Americans, the American Joint Distribution Committee, set up offices in Munich.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they asked people who would want to volunteer to work for them, to do office work or whatever was necessary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was one of the first volunteers.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
